Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: How Texas became American
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bxln
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Mar 1979
Why Mexico still resents losing Texas and her western territories to the US. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.